><menuchoice
><shortcut
> <keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;<keycap
>P</keycap
></keycombo
> </shortcut
> <guimenu
>Messaggio</guimenu
> <guimenuitem
>Stampa...</guimenuitem
> </menuchoice
